    "description": "<p><strong>M</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>r</strong><strong>ke</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>i</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>g M & E 2000 </strong>is a multi-versatile trading supplier company that was incorporated in 26th July 1995 focusing on superior quality construction supplies products with the vision to enhance business image value, product efficiency and ensuring that end-users maximize returns on investment with durable and reliable products through their scope of operations.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Our Core Objectives </strong>are to focus on customizing individual user needs and to provide a wide range of solutions by maximizing superior results in terms of technological and engineering expertise to ensure smooth operational flows and improving productivity standards.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Our Goals and Objectives </strong>are supported by well reputable factories which have decades of experience in terms of engineering expertise, craftsmanship, quality materials, sophisticated manufacturing processes and superior customer service. Our commitment to the industries has helped us to earn a reputation of sales & service with excellence.</p>\n",
